\id GEN FIXTURE - not real Bible content; for adapter tests only
\h Kinohi
\mt1 Kinohi
\c 1
\v 1 He hoailona keia no ka hoao ana o ka mea kakau.
\v 2 O ka olelo Hawaii he olelo nani.
\v 3 Ua hoike ia keia ma ka palapala hoao.
\v 4 He pokole na pauku a pau o ka palapala nei.
\v 5 O ka hopena, ua pau ka hoao ana.
